data.description: Start the new year in your new 3 bedroom home nestled away on a level 1 acre parcel in the Yough School District.  Upon entering you are greeted with an open floor plan, updated flooring, paint, light fixtures and neutral decor.  Kitchen has been updated and includes dishwasher, electric stove and microwave oven.  Full bath on main floor updated to include beautiful walk-in tile shower.  Walk out lower level easily transformed into additional living space, perfect for family/game room, man cave, home office, home gym or kid's playroom and still have plenty of space for storage.  Laundry area on lower level.  Updated windows, newer roof and freshly painted brick exterior give the house great curb appeal. One-car integral garage plus a 24x24 carport for 2 vehicles and additional parking area. Covered back porch ideal for relaxing or entertaining friends and family.  Be ready for summertime fun with the above-ground swimming pool and campfires around the firepit.  Worth the look!
